snippet.title: Sky Sport NZ
snippet.description:
Welcome to SKY Sport NZ's YouTube channel - the only place for a taste of New Zealand's best sporting content.

If you love sport, you'll love the SKY Sport package with SKY Sport NZ. SKY Sport has all of the best international and local sport from around the country and from around the globe. It's the only place you can access such a wide range of sport to suit all tastes with most sport offered live and exclusive. SKY's five dedicated sports channels mean you can enjoy your favourite game or just the highlights 24 hours a day seven days a week.
